					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">I've done some collaborative projects with a group over the internet before, 2 programmers, 1 artist, and 1 musician, and things came together pretty well.  Art and music is pretty easily independant, but code can be a little challenging.  It's good when you can modularize the code. e.g. one person does sound code, another does AI/ character interaction, another does tools, etc.
<br />
<br />I guess in a way, if we use any libraries/code like the famitracker driver its a collaborative effort.</div>

